com.orsoncharts

Class ChartBox3D.ChartBoxFace

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.orsoncharts.graphics3d.Face
      • com.orsoncharts.ChartBox3D.ChartBoxFace
  • Enclosing class:
    ChartBox3D

    public static final class ChartBox3D.ChartBoxFace
extends Face
    A special subclass of Face that is used by the ChartBox3D so that when faces are sorted by z-order, the chart box sides are always drawn first (furthest in the background). Also, these faces track tick marks, values and anchor points.
